init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She was the best dog I have ever had.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Egyptians believed in many gods, and since animals were considered to be living gods, they believed that humans could reincarnate into animals.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: are found in the tombs of pharaohs, because they were thought to be companions in life and death.
